data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This spacious and beautifully updated home offers the perfect blend of modern living and serene countryside charm. Situated on a sprawling 6.53 acre lot, this property is a sanctuary of comfort and style. With over 2000 sq. ft. of living space, you'll have plenty of room to create memorable moments with family and friends. Escape to your private sanctuary with a main floor master bedroom suite. The suite includes ample closet space and a master bathroom that exudes sophistication and relaxation. Cozy up on chilly evenings in front of the inviting gas log fireplace. its warm glow and elegant design create a focal point in the living area, making it an ideal spot for relaxation and entertainment. There's also an expansive bonus room with its own entry which is a versatile space that can be tailored to your unique needs. It's perfect for a home office, guest suite, or entertainment area. On the outside is a massive 32 x 50 pole barn and a 30 x 24 Barn style shed with a great lofted space. Most electrical wires have been pulled but no electric is ran to building.  Whether you're a hobbyist, car enthusiast, or simply need extra storage, this space has you covered. Along with all this many of the big things has been taken care of for you. This home has a 4 year old metal roof, newer furnace, central air, and water heater along with a Watco water system.
